\c 32
\s UElihu uyaqhamuka. Uqala ukumphendula uJobe
\p
\v 1 Lawomadoda amathathu aseyekela ukumphendula uJobe, ngoba wayelungile emehlweni akhe\x + 31.6. 33.9.\x*.
\v 2 Lwaseluvutha ulaka lukaElihu indodana kaBarakeli umBuzi\x + Gen. 22.21. Jer. 25.23.\x*, owosendo lukaRamu\x + Gen. 22.21. Jer. 25.23.\x*. Ulaka lwakhe lwavuthela uJobe ngoba wazilungisisa yena kuloNkulunkulu\x + 4.17. 34.5. 35.2. 40.8.\x*.
\v 3 Ulaka lwakhe lwabavuthela labo abangane bakhe abathathu, ngoba bengatholanga impendulo, kube kanti bamlahla uJobe\x + 8.6. 15.20-35. 22.5.\x*.
\v 4 Kodwa UElihu wayelindele uJobe ekhuluma, ngoba babebadala ngensuku kulaye.
\v 5 UElihu esebonile ukuthi kwakungelampendulo emlonyeni walamadoda amathathu, ulaka lwakhe lwaseluvutha.
\v 6 Ngakho uElihu indodana kaBarakeli umBuzi waphendula wathi:
\p Mina ngingomncinyane ngezinsuku, lina-ke libadala\x + 15.10. 2 Lan. 36.17.\x*. Ngenxa yalokhu bengithikaza, ngesaba ukulitshela\x + Hlab. 19.2.\x* umcabango wami\x + 32.10,17. 36.3. 37.16.\x*.
\v 7 Ngathi: Kakukhulume izinsuku, lobunengi beminyaka bazise inhlakanipho.
\v 8 Isibili umoya ukhona emuntwini\x + 33.4. 34.14.\x*, lokuphefumulela kukaSomandla\x + 35.11. 38.36. 39.17. 1 Kho. 3.12. 4.29. Zaga 2.6. Tshu. 2.26. Dan. 1.17. 2.21. Jak. 1.5.\x* kuyabanika ukuqedisisa\x + 33.4. 34.14.\x*.
\v 9 Abakhulu kabahlakaniphi\x + 32.7. Gen. 25.23.\x* \add ngezikhathi zonke\add*, labalupheleyo \add ka\add*baqedisis\add i\add* isahlulelo\x + 12.20. Mat. 11.25.\x*.
\v 10 Ngakho ngithi: Lalelani kimi; lami ngizatshengisa umcabango wami\x + 32.10,17. 36.3. 37.16.\x*.
\v 11 Khangelani, bengiwalindele amazwi enu, ngabeka indlebe ekukhulumeni kwenu okuhlakaniphileyo, lisadinga amazwi.
\v 12 Yebo, ngalilalela, khangelani-ke, kakho phakathi kwenu omvumisileyo uJobe, owaphenduleyo amazwi akhe\x + 38.18. 31.1.\x*.
\v 13 Hlezi lithi: Sitholile inhlakanipho; nguNkulunkulu ozamxotsha, hatshi umuntu\x + 13.25.\x*.
\v 14 Kodwa kangihlelelanga amazwi, langamazwi enu kangiyikumphendula.
\v 15 Badideka, kabasaphendulanga, basusa amazwi kubo.
\v 16 Ngasengilinda, kodwa kabakhulumanga, ngoba bema, kabasaphendulanga.
\v 17 Lami ngizaphendula ingxenye yami\x + Eks. 18.4.\x*, lami ngitshengise\x + 32.6.\x* umcabango wami\x + 32.10,17. 36.3. 37.16.\x*.
\v 18 Ngoba ngigcwele amazwi, umoya wesisu sami uyangiqhubezela.
\v 19 Khangelani, isisu sami sinjengewayini engavulwanga, njengemigodla emitsha sizadabuka\x + Mat. 9.17. Josh. 9.4.\x*.
\v 20 Ngizakhuluma ukuze ngiphefumule; ngivule indebe zami, ngiphendule.
\v 21 Ake ngingaphakamisi ubuso bomuntu\x + 42.8.\x*, ngingabizi umuntu ngebizo lokubamba amehlo\x + Isa. 44.5. 45.4.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba kangikwazi ukunika amabizo okubamba amehlo; masinyane umenzi wami angangisusa\x + Isa. 44.5. 45.4.\x*.
